Package: openhrp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, liblapack-dev, libblas-dev, libjpeg-dev, libpng-dev, libboost-signals-dev | libpng-dev, libboost-regex-dev, libboost-program-options-dev, libboost-filesystem-dev
Description: Open Architecture Human-centered Robotics Platform version 3
  OpenHRP3 is an integrated software platform for robot simulations and
  software developments. It allows the users to inspect an original robot
  model and control program by dynamics simulation. In addition, OpenHRP3
  provides various software components and calculation libraries that can
  be used for robotics related software developments. 
